data.description: SELLER WILL CONSIDER RENT TO OWN WITH CONSIDERABLE DOWNPAYMENT. NEARLY BRAND-NEW STILL UNDER WARRANTY townhome in Tampa. Don't miss your opportunity to own this 2-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom with 1 CAR GARAGE is located in a BRAND-NEW community and is in immaculate condition. Adequate foyer space with closet. The kitchen features a large island with seating, plenty of cabinets, beautiful Granite countertops, Walk in Pantry and more! The laundry room is off the kitchen and includes a BRAND-NEW WASHER AND DRYER! The Open floor plan combines the Kitchen, Living room, and dining room. Luxury Vinyl plank Flooring throughout the entire first floor and all bathrooms. Enjoy the convenience of a covered lanai. Upstairs you will find a large Master Bedroom with great closet space, beautiful Master bath with dual sinks and enclosed shower. The second bedroom has its own ensuite with a shower-tub combination! Convenient to Downtown Tampa, Shops, Restaurants, Entertainment, Beaches and more!
